room_title: Escape room "The Lucky Lady Saloon" by The Room - Wichita in Wichita
room_description:
You are inside the Lucky Lady Saloon. Somewhere inside this tavern lies the gold from the infamous Black Hat Gangs latest heist.  Patty Oâ€™Miley, Bar Keep and the Lucky Lady proprietor was entrusted with the loot. Problem is Patty was gunned down by a mounted posse about 1 hour east of town. Worse, the James Gang heard about the score and are coming to take it. They were last seen 1 hour to the west!
You and your team need to recover the loot and get out of town before they arrive.
